/*
********The NES PAD*******
* NES strobe pin -> pin 2
* NES clock pin -> pin 3
* NES data pin -> pin 4
*
***The RF24L01 transmitter***
* vcc pin -> 3.3v
* CSN pin -> pin 10
* MOSI pin -> pin 11
* IRQ pin -> pin 8
* GND pin -> pin gnd
* CE pin -> pin 9
* SCK pin -> pin 13
* MISO pin -> pin 12
*
*****The LCD display*****
* LCD pin 1 -> ground
* LCD pin 2 -> 5V
* LCD pin 3 -> 10k pot
* LCD pin 4 -> pin A1
* LCD pin 5 -> ground
* LCD pin 6 -> pin A2
* LCD pin 9 -> pin 5
* LCD pin 11 -> pin A0
* LCD pin 12 -> pin 6
* LCD pin 13 -> pin 7
* LCD pin 14 -> pin A1
* LCD pin 15 -> 5V
* LCD pin 16 -> gnd
*/

